# Unit Testing

## Component Testing

**با Testing Library:**
- Test user interactions
- Test props
- Test events
- Test accessibility

**الگو:**
- Render component
- Query elements (by role, label, text)
- Fire events
- Assert expectations

## Store Testing

**الگو:**
- Test initial state
- Test mutations
- Test derived stores
- Test error handling

## Utility Testing

- Pure functions
- Edge cases (null, empty, invalid)
- Type validation
- Error handling

## Best Practices

- Test behavior, not implementation
- Test user interactions
- Isolate tests (no shared state)
- Clear test names
- AAA pattern
